        <mxCell id="vKg46ZQ0wSFK0trTurh0-11" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=11;" value="&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;Performance:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;map query returns results in &amp;lt; 1s for typical city viewport&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;posts/events return paginated results in (100 results &amp;lt; 1s), results must be queryable with start index n+1&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;Security: basic rate limiting on create endpoints (places/posts/reports) Creating locations, events both 1/10s, (out of scope: rate limiting based on reputation). Posts 1/3s. Reporting 1/2s, 5/24h (subject to scale with userbase) (out of scope, higher rep higher limits)&amp;nbsp; unauthenticated read-only usage provided. Google OAuth2 SSO JWT, (out of scope: other methods, magic link etc)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;Privacy: location permission optional; allow manual city browsing if denied. User must agree to data processing outside of GDPR, limited userbase (email allowlist). Reflect privacy status in policy (collection, why, how long, shared with who). (out of scope: GDPR)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;Auditability: soft delete for content moderation; store who removed it, Only viewable by moderators+, deleted posts/events not visibile to end-users)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;Observability: Collects logs of user activity, (Loki+Grafana) (out of scope: prometheus metrics)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;Maintanability: Modular monolith, testability&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="410" width="310" x="41" y="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
